-- 
Huntsman Reports Ethylene Emissions at Port Neches, Texas, Unit

-- B y   T h e o   M u l l e n
-- 
2011-03-05T21:00:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-05/huntsman-reports-ethylene-emissions-at-port-neches-texas-unit.html
  Huntsman Corp. (HUN)  reported ethylene
emissions today at its Port Neches, Texas, chemical plant after
a mechanical problem in a boiler fan, a filing to Texas
regulators shows.  The problem was resolved after about two hours, the filing
said, and the boiler was restarted.  The Huntsman Port Neches plant is 100 miles (160
kilometers) east of Houston.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Theo Mullen at 
 tmullen11@bloomberg.net  